<view class="page">
  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">核心操作</view>
      <view class="section-desc">先处理最常用的三项内容，效率更高。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="primary-grid">
      <view class="primary-card memory" bindtap="goToMemoryManage">
        <view class="primary-icon">🖼️</view>
        <view class="primary-title">回忆管理</view>
        <view class="primary-desc">上传照片、整理故事，按时间线陪老人回看人生片段。</view>
      </view>

      <view class="primary-card members" bindtap="goToMembers">
        <view class="primary-icon">👨‍👩‍👧</view>
        <view class="primary-title">家庭成员</view>
        <view class="primary-desc">维护家属资料和关系信息，完善家庭陪伴网络。</view>
      </view>

      <view class="primary-card health" bindtap="goToHealthManage">
        <view class="primary-icon">❤️</view>
        <view class="primary-title">健康管理</view>
        <view class="primary-desc">查看用药、健康记录和每日照护信息。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">更多服务</view>
      <view class="section-desc">资料完善、留言沟通和生活指引都放在这里。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="service-list">
      <view class="service-card" bindtap="goToProfile">
        <view class="service-left">
          <view class="service-icon profile">🪪</view>
          <view class="service-copy">
            <view class="service-title">老人资料</view>
            <view class="service-desc">完善身份信息、联系电话和重要资料。</view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="service-arrow">></view>
      </view>

      <view class="service-card" bindtap="goToMessageBoard">
        <view class="service-left">
          <view class="service-icon message">💬</view>
          <view class="service-copy">
            <view class="service-title">家人留言板</view>
            <view class="service-desc">给 {{elderName}} 留下语音和文字，保持温暖联系。</view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="service-arrow">></view>
      </view>

      <view class="service-card" bindtap="goToLifeGuides">
        <view class="service-left">
          <view class="service-icon guide">🧰</view>
          <view class="service-copy">
            <view class="service-title">生活小助手</view>
            <view class="service-desc">上传家电和常用物品教程，帮助老人独立操作。</view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="service-arrow">></view>
      </view>

      <view class="service-card" bindtap="goToBindPage">
        <view class="service-left">
          <view class="service-icon bind">🔗</view>
          <view class="service-copy">
            <view class="service-title">绑定老人</view>
            <view class="service-desc">{{hasBoundElder ? "查看当前绑定状态，必要时重新发起绑定流程。" : "先完成绑定，再开启后续管理功能。"}}</view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="service-arrow">></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tip-card">
    <view class="tip-title">✨ 使用建议</view>
    <view class="tip-line">先完善老人资料，再上传回忆内容，家属协作会更顺畅。</view>
    <view class="tip-line">上传后的内容会同步显示在老人端，方便老人随时查看和回忆。</view>
  </view>
</view>
